Name:                dynamic-plot
Version:             0.1
Category:            graphics
Synopsis:            Interactive diagram windows
Description:         When plotting functions etc., it is often not known a priori what
                     range should be displayed, what resolution is needed etc.. The
                     most efficient way to set these parameters is in an interactive
                     window.
